@startuml
title TestForge - Ciclo de Vida da FailureSignature na Curadoria Multiagente

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
  FontColor Black
}

[*] --> DETECTED : execution_failed / capture_failure_context

state DETECTED
state NORMALIZED
state CLASSIFIED
state EVIDENCE_PACKAGED
state AGENT_SELECTED
state PATCH_PROPOSED
state PATCH_VALIDATING
state PATCH_REJECTED
state PATCH_APPLIED_TEMPORARILY
state REEXECUTING
state PASSED_STEP
state PROGRESSED
state STAGNATED
state REGRESSED
state ERROR_CHANGED
state UNRESOLVED
state ROLLED_BACK
state ESCALATED_TO_LLM
state ESCALATED_TO_MANUAL_REVIEW
state RESOLVED
state ABANDONED

DETECTED --> NORMALIZED : normalize_failure / build_failure_signature_json
NORMALIZED --> CLASSIFIED : classify_failure / assign_failure_family
CLASSIFIED --> EVIDENCE_PACKAGED : package_evidence / reuse_original_recording_and_run_artifacts
EVIDENCE_PACKAGED --> AGENT_SELECTED : evidence_ready / consult_knowledge_base_and_select_agent
AGENT_SELECTED --> PATCH_PROPOSED : agent_selected / propose_deterministic_patch
PATCH_PROPOSED --> PATCH_VALIDATING : patch_created / validate_patch

PATCH_VALIDATING --> PATCH_REJECTED : patch_invalid / persist_rejection_reason
PATCH_VALIDATING --> PATCH_APPLIED_TEMPORARILY : patch_valid / apply_to_temporary_version

PATCH_REJECTED --> AGENT_SELECTED : deterministic_strategy_available / select_alternative_agent_or_strategy
PATCH_REJECTED --> UNRESOLVED : no_valid_deterministic_patch / mark_unresolved_candidate

PATCH_APPLIED_TEMPORARILY --> REEXECUTING : temporary_version_ready / rerun_checkpoint_or_script

REEXECUTING --> PASSED_STEP : step_passed / compare_with_previous_failure
REEXECUTING --> PROGRESSED : execution_advanced / create_progress_checkpoint
REEXECUTING --> STAGNATED : no_progress / keep_failure_signature_active
REEXECUTING --> REGRESSED : regression_detected / trigger_rollback
REEXECUTING --> ERROR_CHANGED : error_signature_changed / require_reclassification
REEXECUTING --> UNRESOLVED : no_solution_found / check_limits_and_remaining_strategies

PASSED_STEP --> RESOLVED : failure_removed / accept_patch_and_register_pattern

PROGRESSED --> AGENT_SELECTED : remaining_failure_exists / select_next_agent_or_strategy
PROGRESSED --> RESOLVED : flow_completed / accept_patch_chain_and_register_pattern

STAGNATED --> AGENT_SELECTED : alternative_deterministic_strategy_available / try_next_strategy
STAGNATED --> UNRESOLVED : deterministic_strategy_exhausted / mark_unresolved

REGRESSED --> ROLLED_BACK : rollback_required / restore_last_stable_version
ROLLED_BACK --> AGENT_SELECTED : rollback_completed / select_safer_strategy
ROLLED_BACK --> UNRESOLVED : no_safe_strategy_remaining / mark_unresolved

ERROR_CHANGED --> CLASSIFIED : reclassify_required / rebuild_failure_signature_context

UNRESOLVED --> AGENT_SELECTED : deterministic_strategy_available / retry_with_next_strategy
UNRESOLVED --> ESCALATED_TO_LLM : deterministic_limit_exceeded / controlled_llm_fallback
UNRESOLVED --> ESCALATED_TO_MANUAL_REVIEW : llm_disabled_by_policy / request_human_review

ESCALATED_TO_LLM --> PATCH_PROPOSED : llm_suggested_candidate / validate_like_deterministic_patch
ESCALATED_TO_LLM --> ESCALATED_TO_MANUAL_REVIEW : no_valid_llm_solution / request_human_review
ESCALATED_TO_LLM --> ABANDONED : llm_limit_exceeded / preserve_unresolved_report

ESCALATED_TO_MANUAL_REVIEW --> PATCH_PROPOSED : human_hint_provided / create_candidate_patch
ESCALATED_TO_MANUAL_REVIEW --> ABANDONED : no_solution_available / close_failure_as_abandoned

RESOLVED --> [*] : resolved_pattern_registered
ABANDONED --> [*] : unresolved_history_preserved

DETECTED --> ABANDONED : unrecoverable_missing_evidence
NORMALIZED --> ABANDONED : normalization_impossible
CLASSIFIED --> ABANDONED : classification_blocked_by_invalid_signature
EVIDENCE_PACKAGED --> ABANDONED : evidence_package_insufficient
AGENT_SELECTED --> ABANDONED : no_agent_available
PATCH_APPLIED_TEMPORARILY --> ROLLED_BACK : temporary_version_corrupted / rollback
REEXECUTING --> ABANDONED : unrecoverable_execution_infrastructure_error

note right of EVIDENCE_PACKAGED
  O pacote de evidências deve reutilizar a gravação
  e os artefatos originais da sessão:
  - session_raw.json
  - session_normalized.json
  - selector_candidates.json
  - fingerprint_initial.json
  - fingerprint_final.json
  - screenshots, DOM, rede, console, frames,
    shadow DOM, storage e trace.

  A curadoria não pode ignorar o contexto coletado
  durante a interação humana.
end note

note right of REGRESSED
  REGRESSED significa que o patch piorou o fluxo,
  quebrou steps previamente válidos ou removeu
  comportamento necessário.

  Neste estado o rollback é obrigatório antes de
  qualquer nova tentativa.
end note

note right of ERROR_CHANGED
  ERROR_CHANGED significa que a assinatura da falha
  mudou após uma tentativa.

  A falha deve voltar para CLASSIFIED para que a nova
  família seja identificada e roteada para o agente correto.
end note

note right of ESCALATED_TO_LLM
  O LLM é fallback controlado.

  Ele só é acionado depois que as estratégias
  determinísticas aplicáveis foram tentadas ou esgotadas.
  Sua saída é apenas hipótese ou patch candidato e deve
  passar por PATCH_VALIDATING antes de qualquer execução.
end note

note right of RESOLVED
  RESOLVED exige evidência de validação:
  - patch aceito;
  - execução comparativa bem-sucedida;
  - checkpoint criado;
  - padrão aprendido registrado na KnowledgeBase;
  - regra candidata de healing rastreável.
end note

@enduml
